==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Browning
<hw>Brown"ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The act or operation
of giving a brown color, as to gun barrels, etc.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Masonry)</fld> <def>A smooth coat of brown mortar,
usually the second coat, and the preparation for the finishing coat of
plaster.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Brownish</ent>⟦br⟧
